<p class="mt-[2rem] font-light text-lg ml-[9rem]">Updated 31 May 2022</p>

<p class="mt-[2rem] font-light text-lg ml-[9rem]">On 11 March 2020, the World Health Organization (WHO) declared the outbreak of <br>
  coronavirus, known as COVID-19, to be a global pandemic. Since then, the outbreak  <br> 
