</p>

<p class="mt-[2rem] font-light text-lg ml-[9rem]">
  In response, we have provided the following coverage for COVID-19 under our <br> 
  extenuating circumstances policy to help protect our community and provide peace <br> 
  of mind.
</p>


<div class=" border-[1.5px] rounded-xl p-[16px] pl-[1rem] mt-[3rem] ml-[9rem] w-[47rem]">
